# Git Push

**Every time** you complete an editing session, **push to git**:

1. Run `git status` - if there are uncommitted changes, stage and commit them
2. Run `git push`

Do not end an editing session without pushing. The user has stated this explicitly; do not skip it or wait to be asked.
